Pyongyang Control, Pyongyang Control.

00:23:51.869 --> 00:23:54.872
This is Japan Airways 351.

00:23:54.955 --> 00:23:56.248
Radio check.

00:23:59.334 --> 00:24:02.421
Pyongyang Control, Pyongyang Control,

00:24:02.504 --> 00:24:05.257
this is Japan Airways 351.

00:24:05.924 --> 00:24:07.176
Radio check.

00:24:22.483 --> 00:24:26.320
Japan Airways 351,
this is Pyongyang Control. Loud and clear.

